title: Ep - 118 - 90 DAY FIANCÉ: BEFORE THE 90 DAYS PREMIERE REVIEW
description:
Ronnie Karam, co-host of Watch What Crappens and Rose Pricks podcast helps Kate review the season premiere of 90 Day Fiancé: Before the 90 Days. This prequel to TLC’s “90 Day Fiancé” features couples who have an existing relationship online, but have never met in person. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
